      "fullContent": "AI at Meta on X: \"Straight from @finkd — Muse Spark 1.1 is live.\" / X\nPost\nLog in Sign up\nPost\nAI at Meta\n@AIatMeta\nStraight from @ finkd — Muse Spark 1.1 is live.\nMark Zuckerberg\n@finkd\n7月9日\n(1) Today we're releasing Muse Spark 1.1 -- a strong agentic and coding model at a very low price. It's available through our new Meta Model API and in Meta AI.\n14:00 · 2026年7月9日 18.3万 Views\n8 8 88\n8 8 88\n2 . 2 K 2.2K\n1 3 7 137\nRead 88 replies\nSign up with Google Sign up with Apple Create account\nBy signing up, you agree to the Terms of Service and Privacy Policy , including Cookie Use.\nRelevant people\nAI at Meta @ AIatMeta Follow\nTrending now\nDon't miss what's happening\nPeople on X are the first to know.\nLog in Sign up"
