      "id": "cmrd9x7xz01wzih4bch5uoywh",
      "title": "NVIDIA 发布 Nemotron-Labs-3-Puzzle-75B-A9B：压缩混合 MoE 模型，服务器吞吐量提升 2.03 倍",
      "title_en": "NVIDIA Releases Nemotron-Labs-3-Puzzle-75B-A9B： A Compressed Hybrid MoE LLM Delivering 2.03x Server Throughput at Matched User Throughput",
      "url": "https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/07/09/nvidia-releases-nemotron-labs-3-puzzle-75b-a9b-a-compressed-hybrid-moe-llm-delivering-2-03x-server-throughput-at-matched-user-throughput",
