      "title": "中国拟限制外国访问最强AI模型",
      "title_en": "🇨🇳This is bad news. Now， frontier open source access also will probably no more be available for a…",
      "url": "https://x.com/rohanpaul_ai/status/2074512389526237609",
      "permalink": "https://aihot.virxact.com/items/cmrasueu500qmihog3d8up11t",
