      "title": "智能免费，然后呢？--Data Systems for， of， and by Agents",
      "title_en": "Intelligence is Free， Now What？ <br> Data Systems for， of， and by Agents",
      "url": "http://bair.berkeley.edu/blog/2026/07/07/intelligence-is-free-now-what",
      "permalink": "https://aihot.virxact.com/items/cmrawne9601nfihogtkxwy0bs",
      "source": "BAIR：Berkeley AI Research Blog",
      "publishedAt": "2026-07-07T09:00:00.000Z",
      "summary": "AI推理成本急剧下降。GPT-4级能力从2023年初每百万token约30美元降至今天不到1美元，部分供应商已低于0.10美元。推理价格每年下降9至900倍，中位数约50倍。知识工作级智能即将近乎免费。这给数据系统带来三重变革：面向智能体的数据系统需支持智能体推测式探索--单个",
